data.description: SR 93 - 22 acres - Hocking County. Land for sale in Hocking County, Ohio. Located off of State Route 93 just under 2.5 miles south of Downtown Logan and 10.5 miles from Old Mans Cave. Take advantage of this rare opportunity to purchase a great property in the Hocking Hills that is ready for your new cabin or forever home. If you have been looking for a weekend retreat or a place to build your dream home in the Hocking Hills this one could be for you. Current annual taxes are $1352.34, and any mineral interest owned by the seller will be transferred.
